Enclosing class:
NamedGraphSetImpl
protected class NamedGraphSetImpl.UnionGraph
extends MultiUnion

Subclass of MultiUnion that allows the list of member graphs to be directly passed to the constructor. When we later change the list (add or remove graphs from the NamedGraphSet), the member list of the MultiUnion is automatically updated.

NOTE This is a hack.
